						"html": "<div class=\"column\">*</div>",
						"classes": "column p-6 rounded-5 bg-light mb-18",
						"droppable": true,
						"children": {
							"content:wysiwyg_basic:0:29": {
								"icon": "outdent",
								"name": "WYSIWYG",
								"type": "wysiwyg_basic",
								"html": "<p>The strength of our service in this community is fueled by the neighbors who serve alongside us. Whether you are looking to give back on a Saturday morning or want to find a consistent way to share your professional skills, we make it simple to connect your heart for service with a local need.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>We utilize a digital volunteer portal that allows you to manage your own journey. From here, you can see exactly where help is needed today, sign up for shifts that fit your schedule, and track your total hours of impact in real-time.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p><strong>View Local Needs</strong></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://volunteer.central.salvationarmyusa.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Search Nearby Opportunities</a></p>",
